<dl id="n53122m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n53" href="#n53122m">N53 (VI.B.46)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n53all.htm#n53122m"> 122(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> s of Maya ~</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Or, la reine <mark>M&acirc;y&acirc;</mark> ne put supporter longtemps la joie que lui donnait <mark>son fils</mark>: il avait sept jours seulement qu&apos;elle mourut pour la terre, et qu&apos;elle monta au ciel, parmi les Dieux. <small> A. Ferdinand Herold, <a name="AFHB" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#AFHB"><cite title="source">La Vie Du Bouddha</cite></a> (1922) 21</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: After seven days Maya, Siddharta&apos;s mother, died and was taken into the heavens. </mm> </dd></dl>
